      "titleText": "⚠️ Legal Reminder",
      "titleColor": "#00ff41",
      "titleSize": 48,
      "subtitleText": "",
      "subtitleColor": "#2a6b3a",
      "bodyText": "Only operate against systems you have explicit written authorisation to test. Unauthorised access is illegal in virtually every jurisdiction. Always work under a signed Rules of Engagement (RoE) document.",
